	(67, 89, 'the pasanger', 8, '퓨전/기타', '성인', '화, 수', 2, '유니티', 25, '베스트리그', 'Rosenberg was born on 17 May 1984[2][3] in Brighton & Hove, East Sussex, England to an English mother and an American father, Gerard Rosenberg, originally from Vineland, New Jersey.[4][5] His father is Jewish.[6] Rosenberg learned classical guitar at a young age, and around 14–15 started to wri', 'images/cover_image/로맨스_07.jpg', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'key 4', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, '2016-01-29 02:33:58', '2016-01-29 02:33:58'),
